# ray-man
A Collection of manuals for ray-userland and related guides.

# Installation
To install `ray-man` to use:
```
npm i -g ray-man
```
> The `ray-man` program works in all oprating systems that support NodeJS and NPM.

# Usage
To check version:
```
ray-man -v
```

To check the README.md of a package hosted at Github's Ray6464 account use:
```
ray-man -d package-name
```

To update database of docs:
```
ray-man -u
```

To get a list of locally installed docs:
```
ray-man -l
```

